{"tid":1174290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁香港牌呢？】特朗普啟用新武器　打新疆「人權牌」","createTime":"2019-05-27T17:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T04:45:28.000Z","uid":226548,"like":315,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"9c10238909a4e93f68def3f8e58e9fdac14a6ff4","tid":1174290,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T17:45:54.000Z","msg":"美國連日來對中國電訊巨頭華為進行全面封殺，除了華為，特朗普政府被指有意制裁中國監控設備龍頭生產商&mdash;&mdash;海康威視等5間中資公司，原因是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">它們的產品被指「幫助」中國政府限制新疆維吾爾族人的自由。</span></strong>外界關注，報道若屬實，意味着特朗普再啟動一條遏制中國的新戰線&mdash;&mdash;「人權牌」。<br />\n<br />\n分析續指，在白宮擬用人權為由制裁海康威視之前，美國佛羅里達州共和党參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）和另外16名來自兩黨的議員，早在2018年8月曾致信國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）和財政部長姆努欽（Steven Mnuchin），要求美國政府關注新疆再教育營問題，以經濟制裁制止中國官方繼續限制維吾爾族人的自由。"},{"pid":"1a24c4d013ce61f3cb3f156a1dbd42a5f0c2a1a9","tid":1174290,"uid":345,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T17:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3064d2c5f1fc04bd9fc61c3107ea7f61117eaf","tid":1174290,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T17:46:59.000Z","msg":"<ins><a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/議事廳/333598/中美貿易戰-特朗普啟用新武器-亮-人權牌-打貿易戰\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B3%2F333598%2F%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%95%9F%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8-%E4%BA%AE-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E7%89%8C-%E6%89%93%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=3ff37f2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/議事廳/333598/中美貿易戰-特朗普啟用新武器-亮-人權牌-打貿易戰</a></ins>"},{"pid":"9a4a34c0ebbc25eab6447ca369